Sun Jul 12 19:07:36 UTC 2026 - Martin Pluskal <mpluskal@suse.com>

- Initial package python-xgrammar 0.2.3
  * Efficient, flexible and portable structured generation engine for
    constrained LLM decoding against JSON schemas, regex and grammars
